  "time_ut": 1661245610,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d86\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d86\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0d9a\u0dba\u0ddd \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dda \u0db6\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The civil guards who were on guard fired at the battery of the electric fence",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Vilachchiya Police said that two Civil Defense Force soldiers and a farmer were arrested in connection with an incident of theft of an energiser (a machine that reduces the electric current and makes it intermittent) which was installed in an electric fence built to prevent wild elephants from invading the village.",
        "Police say that while these two Civil Defense Force soldiers were on duty for the security of the generator attached to the electric fence in Mannaram Junction, Degahwa area, someone or a group of people broke the front door of the room where it was installed and committed this theft.",
        "In this regard, after an animal site security officer made a complaint to the Mahavilachchi police, the civil defense force soldiers and the farmer were arrested.",
        "The police say that it is revealed that the Civil Defense Force soldiers had some knowledge regarding this theft and that the third suspect, the person who lives by farming, is a resident of this vicinity."
      ],
